{
  "stem": "2966.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at that time, I was always with my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I got-- I got separated with him in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I volunteered to go to that barrack with the sick people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was there for a couple days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And suddenly, my father showed up from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't even know where he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were reunited together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In that place, I was still doing pretty good physically.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I started helping out the guy that was in charge of the barrack because we had German prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Some were criminals, some were political.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But they always were kapos, and they were always in charge of something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they had it pretty good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I started helping him out with the-- handing out the soup and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So there was always a little extra soup left over that they shared with myself and my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And-- but there was no future there to survive at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they were calling for a transport to go someplace else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "My father and myself volunteered, and we went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that must have been, like, I'd say, December 31 or January 1 of 1945 already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We went to Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Sachsenhausen was a very big camp, tremendously big camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was a showcase of the great German republic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They used to bring Red Cross people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They used to bring [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people from Switzerland to examine the camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was tremendous camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "When we arrived there, I was sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I have such a nature that I can feel whenever I have temperature.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "When we arrived there, we were separated or segregated, who was going where.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
